data.eml:eml: A new species of Gorogobius (Perciformes: Gobiidae) from São Tomé Islands

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Ić, Marcelo Kova Č, Schliewen, Ulrich K. (2008): A new species of Gorogobius (Perciformes: Gobiidae) from São Tomé Islands. Zootaxa 1686: 29-36, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.180510
